Compile with: gcc -Wall -o testBMP085 ./smbus.c ./testBMP085.c


Circuit detail:
	
	SDA	- 	P1-03 / IC20-SDA
	SCL	- 	P1-05 / IC20_SCL
	XCLR	- 	Not Connected
	EOC	-	Not Connected
	GND	-	P1-06 / GND
	VCC	- 	P1-01 / 3.3V
	
	Note: Make sure you use P1-01 / 3.3V NOT the 5V pin.
